{
  "body": "The https://docs.perl6.org/routine/run docs are a page long and show a bunch of stuff, but unless you read all of them and notice the very last sentence mentioning `Proc`, you may miss that `run` takes arguments like `:enc` and stuff.\r\n\r\nThose should be at least hinted at in the shown signature and perhaps the note that it takes a bunch of args should be moved closer to the start of the prose.",
